Rmin: Midpoint of innermost radial bin used in entropy fits
Rmax: Midpoint of outermost bin used in entropy fit
K0: Entropy excess from least squares fit
K100: entropy at 100 kpc from least squares fit
Alpha: power law entropy profile from least squares fit
ChiSq: estimated reduced chi square from least squares
K100_PL: entropy at 100 kpc fo single power law model least squares fitting
K100err_PL: error on entropy at 100 kpc for single power law model
Alpha_PL: single power law entropy slope from least squares fitting
AlphaErr_PL: error on single power law entropy slope
ChiSq_PL: reduced chi square to single power law from least squares fitting
Npts: Number of radial entropy points in fit
Pt Src Flag: pt src (within central 10" excluded from spectral analysis)
